<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I need _pdfpageClass property  to specify which Zend_Pdf_Page object is used to render page.
When you use Zend_Db_Table  you can specify  which class you want to use to render row and rowSet.</p>

<p>It would be nice to have the samething with Zend_Pdf allowing to set which Zend_Pdf_Page object you want to use.</p>

<p>I've extended the Zend_Pdf_Object  to implement FPDF like methods.  It works like a charm for new page  but  If want to load a template using  my custom Zend_Pdf_Page object  I can't  !
The default Zend_Pdf_Page  object is used !</p>

<p>Thank you</p>

